I'm 16. I used to be the youngest in a group, but I'm the oldest here.

39
00:01:09,874 --> 00:01:12,073
- I'm Park Sung On. Nice to see you. - That was good.

40
00:01:12,074 --> 00:01:13,404
He really did a great job.

41
00:01:13,974 --> 00:01:16,444
- He came on the show not long ago. - Right.

42
00:01:17,644 --> 00:01:20,113
