43
00:01:20,114 --> 00:01:21,983
Kim Tae Yeon. And I'm 15.

44
00:01:21,984 --> 00:01:23,553
- It's nice to meet you all. - So he's the youngest.

45
00:01:23,554 --> 00:01:24,983
Welcome!

46
00:01:24,984 --> 00:01:26,554
She's a top star.

47
00:01:27,324 --> 00:01:29,454
- I... - Welcome.

48
