I used to dream of becoming the president's husband.

49
00:01:32,024 --> 00:01:33,563
I'm Cheon Mu, and I'm 12.

50
00:01:33,564 --> 00:01:35,763
(Lee Cheon Mu, age 12, the young Gwan Sik)

51
00:01:35,764 --> 00:01:37,433
- He played the young Gwan Sik. - This is amazing.

52
