107
00:03:39,824 --> 00:03:42,793
- Ho Dong is the male host. - Yes.

108
00:03:42,794 --> 00:03:44,523
- And she's the female host. - She's a main host.

109
00:03:44,524 --> 00:03:47,063
She's the female host of the show.

110
00:03:47,064 --> 00:03:49,494
Su Yeon, why were you scared of him at first?

111
00:03:49,734 --> 00:03:51,863
I'm small...

112
00:03:51,864 --> 00:03:53,403
