116
00:03:59,244 --> 00:04:00,743
- He was cute but scary. - She suddenly started...

117
00:04:00,744 --> 00:04:01,843
She suddenly started speaking formally.

118
00:04:01,844 --> 00:04:04,613
- She tried to say nice things. - At first...

119
00:04:04,614 --> 00:04:05,643
- We're all friends here. - Oh, right.

120
00:04:05,644 --> 00:04:07,113
- We're all friends. - I mean, he was scary.

121
00:04:07,114 --> 00:04:09,353
- I spoke formally too earlier. - She's my co-host.

122
00:04:09,354 --> 00:04:11,853
Ji Yul and Min Ho, you two are my close friends.

123
00:04:11,854 --> 00:04:13,583
- Right? - Yes, that's right.

124
00:04:13,584 --> 00:04:16,823
Soo Geun, Ji Yul, and I starred on "Cute Trot Expedition..."

125
00:04:16,824 --> 00:04:19,093
- where we went on overnight trips. - Yes. The show lasted for long.

126
00:04:19,094 --> 00:04:21,664
- We did the show for three months. - "Cute Trot Expedition?"

127
00:04:21,994 --> 00:04:23,793
Every night,

128
00:04:23,794 --> 00:04:27,504
Soo Geun asked me to step on his back.

129
00:04:28,474 --> 00:04:30,234
He wouldn't let me go.

130
00:04:30,504 --> 00:04:33,303
- "Step on here for a bit longer." - That must not be a lie.

131
00:04:33,304 --> 00:04:35,614
- He asked for it every day. - Did I?

132
00:04:36,344 --> 00:04:37,574
- It was exhausting. - Min Ho must've been stressed.

133
00:04:38,514 --> 00:04:40,743
Why did you ask him to step on your back?

134
