I stepped on my father's back when I was little.

135
00:04:44,184 --> 00:04:46,323
And weirdly, it felt good when he stepped on my back.

136
00:04:46,324 --> 00:04:48,954
It brought me back the memories of you trampling me before.

137
00:04:49,624 --> 00:04:52,064
Ho Dong often trampled me behind a folding screen.

138
00:04:52,764 --> 00:04:54,424
Do you want me to step on your back now?

139
00:04:55,394 --> 00:04:57,593
Thank you for saying that, Min Ho.

140
00:04:57,594 --> 00:05:00,163
Sung On, we met on the show not long ago.

141
00:05:00,164 --> 00:05:01,363
- Oh, right. - Yes.

142
00:05:01,364 --> 00:05:03,033
