147
00:05:11,784 --> 00:05:14,213
So I'm worried if my head looks too big on the screen.

148
00:05:14,214 --> 00:05:16,213
- Don't worry about such a thing. - It's relatively big.

149
00:05:16,214 --> 00:05:18,013
Sung On, looking at you from here,

150
00:05:18,014 --> 00:05:19,923
- you look like a middle-aged man. - Right.

151
00:05:19,924 --> 00:05:21,553
