153
00:05:22,854 --> 00:05:24,193
for the Children's Day special?

154
00:05:24,194 --> 00:05:25,893
- Like an adult among child stars... - I feel like I should be with you,

155
00:05:25,894 --> 00:05:27,123
- Right. - not here.

156
00:05:27,124 --> 00:05:30,563
Tae Yeon, Cheon Mu, and Ji Woo,

157
00:05:30,564 --> 00:05:33,833
this is your first time meeting us, right?

158
00:05:33,834 --> 00:05:35,903
Tae Yeon, this must be your first time on a variety show.

159
00:05:35,904 --> 00:05:37,133
This is my first time.

160
00:05:37,134 --> 00:05:38,473
Tae Yeon, why are you lying?

161
00:05:38,474 --> 00:05:39,704
