163
00:05:43,014 --> 00:05:44,614
- He's talking about dolhareubang. - He's always there.

164
00:05:44,944 --> 00:05:47,083
- Soo Geun is right. - That's hilarious.

165
00:05:47,084 --> 00:05:48,554
- He's right there. - Tae Yeon.

166
00:05:48,884 --> 00:05:51,313
- He appears in your drama. - Right. His footage is included...

167
00:05:51,314 --> 00:05:52,723
- That's right. - when he was a ssireum player.

168
00:05:52,724 --> 00:05:54,783
- His footage is included. - I mean...

169
00:05:54,784 --> 00:05:55,823
Tae Yeon, I'm really disappointed.

170
00:05:55,824 --> 00:05:57,624
Why didn't you invite me to the wrap-up party?

171
00:05:58,194 --> 00:05:59,693
