172
00:05:59,694 --> 00:06:01,063
Ho Dong appears in the drama.

173
00:06:01,064 --> 00:06:03,364
I appear in the drama "When Life Gives You Tangerines."

174
00:06:03,864 --> 00:06:04,864
Do you know that?

175
00:06:04,865 --> 00:06:07,533
- No, I don't know. - She's scared.

176
00:06:07,534 --> 00:06:09,373
Does Ho Dong appear in the drama?

177
00:06:09,374 --> 00:06:12,143
- If it's your first time hearing... - His footage was on a TV screen.

178
00:06:12,144 --> 00:06:13,444
