182
00:06:19,984 --> 00:06:22,513
Ji Woo, you can just do whatever the others do...

183
00:06:22,514 --> 00:06:23,983
when they do something, okay?

184
00:06:23,984 --> 00:06:25,583
You can just raise your hand when they do.

185
00:06:25,584 --> 00:06:27,624
Look at Ji Woo's teeth. He lost teeth here.

186
00:06:28,454 --> 00:06:30,423
- He's so cute. - He's cute.

187
00:06:30,424 --> 00:06:31,453
- He's so cute. - Indeed.

188
00:06:31,454 --> 00:06:32,563
- How cute. - It's okay.

189
00:06:32,564 --> 00:06:34,823
Oh, right. Jang Hoon, don't you remember me?

190
00:06:34,824 --> 00:06:35,893
- What? - Oh, gosh.

191
00:06:35,894 --> 00:06:37,793
- Is there a story we don't know? - Did he play on your team?

192
00:06:37,794 --> 00:06:38,863
- No, he didn't. - On his basketball team?

193
00:06:38,864 --> 00:06:40,204
- Cheonmu Stephanie, the singer? - As for Cheon Mu,

194
00:06:40,504 --> 00:06:42,803
I can only recognize him from the drama...

195
00:06:42,804 --> 00:06:45,743
- "When Life Gives You Tangerines." - What?

196
00:06:45,744 --> 00:06:47,503
- I'm a little disappointed. - Have they met before?

197
00:06:47,504 --> 00:06:49,743
- Four years ago, - He can't remember meeting him.

198
00:06:49,744 --> 00:06:51,013
we shot a TV commercial together.

199
00:06:51,014 --> 00:06:52,714
- Four years ago? - Gosh. He can't remember it.

200
00:06:53,184 --> 00:06:55,783
- That's unbelievable. - That's so disappointing.

201
00:06:55,784 --> 00:06:56,784
That's really not cool.

202
00:06:56,785 --> 00:06:58,383
(Did he forget me completely?)

203
00:06:58,384 --> 00:06:59,823
- It's unbelievable, right? - It's so disappointing.

204
00:06:59,824 --> 00:07:03,223
- What... What TV commercial was it? - Unbelievable.

205
00:07:03,224 --> 00:07:04,693
- A cookie commercial. - I see.

206
00:07:04,694 --> 00:07:05,794
A cookie commercial?

207
00:07:07,164 --> 00:07:08,523
Shall we dip another one in milk?

208
00:07:08,524 --> 00:07:09,864
- Sounds great! - Sounds great!

209
00:07:10,194 --> 00:07:11,194
(Cheon Mu, Jang Hoon)

210
00:07:11,195 --> 00:07:13,333
- There he is. - You're supposed to remember him.

211
00:07:13,334 --> 00:07:14,963
- How could you not remember that? - My gosh.

212
00:07:14,964 --> 00:07:16,033
You two acted in the same commercial.

213
00:07:16,034 --> 00:07:17,573
- I've seen that commercial. - But his hairstyle...

214
00:07:17,574 --> 00:07:19,704
- I've seen it too. - He had a different hairstyle then.

215
00:07:20,904 --> 00:07:22,443
- Hold on. - Don't you remember him, still?

216
00:07:22,444 --> 00:07:24,643
- He became a lot more handsome. - He's handsome.

217
00:07:24,644 --> 00:07:26,583
Now that I saw that footage, I remember him.

218
00:07:26,584 --> 00:07:29,253
I didn't know it was you, Cheon Mu. I'm sorry.

219
00:07:29,254 --> 00:07:30,684
- How was Jang Hoon? - Exactly.

220
00:07:31,484 --> 00:07:33,483
Unlike my expectation, he was very kind and nice.

221
00:07:33,484 --> 00:07:34,484
- Unlike your expectation? - It was unexpected?

222
00:07:34,485 --> 00:07:35,493
That's right.

223
00:07:35,494 --> 00:07:37,523
- How did you expect him to be? - I thought...

224
00:07:37,524 --> 00:07:38,763
I guess you thought of him as bad.

225
00:07:38,764 --> 00:07:41,724
No, I didn't. Also, there was something cool about him.

226
00:07:42,064 --> 00:07:43,694
Most people...

227
00:07:44,194 --> 00:07:46,603
